         2  ! %Name     ! variabel ! variabel ! links 
         3  ! &Name&&&  ! fest     ! fest     ! links 
         4  ! %Name%%%  ! variabel ! fest     ! links 
         5  ! &&&Name&  ! fest     ! fest     ! rechts 
